Description: Bareos plugin for Proxmox VE VM backup via vzdump
 Provides a Bareos File Daemon plugin that backs up Proxmox VE virtual
 machines using vzdump --stdout. Includes the Python plugin
 (bareos_fd_proxmox), the vzdump-bareos GID-fix wrapper (required because
 bareos-fd runs as gid=bareos while pmxcfs requires gid=0 on its IPC socket),
 and the systemd drop-in to reload bareos-filedaemon after install.

